cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.SE

The paper discusses the detection of DDoS malware in IoT environments using a lightweight convolutional neural network. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) as it deals with identifying and preventing attacks on IoT devices. The use of image recognition also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper involves the networking and communication aspects of IoT devices (cs.NI) and the development of software systems (cs.SE).
